short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: View Minneapolis home energy scores as you browse Zillow

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
***Zillow recently redesigned its website, we are working to update the extension to work with the new layout***

Home energy scores are added to Zillow search results. You can also see more details about a home’s insulation and heating system by clicking on an individual listing. 

All data comes from Minneapolis’ Truth In Sale of Housing (TISH) energy disclosure reports.
